{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil, Ketika Mata Melihat Dunia yang Berbeda","content":"\n<p>Bagaimana rasanya kalau kamu terbangun dari sakit dan melihat dunia yang berbeda? Bukan. Bukan dunia alien. Tapi kamu melihat banyak orang. Bukan orang biasa, melainkan &#8220;mereka&#8221; yang seharusnya sudah berbeda dunia. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56751\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/attachment/6-214/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Saat aku terbangun&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Saat aku terbangun\" class=\"wp-image-56751\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Takut? Ngeri? Ingin menangis? Atau semua campur aduk jadi satu hingga rasanya sulit saat ingin berucap? Mungkin itu juga yang dirasakan oleh Indriya kecil. Saat dia menyadari bahwa dia bisa melihat mereka. Saat dia sadar bahwa semua tidak lagi sama. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56754\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/attachment/9-117/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Percakapan dengan Suster&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1.jpg\" alt=\"Percakapan dengan suster\" class=\"wp-image-56754\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Melihat hantu mungkin sudah jadi hal biasa buat Indriya seorang gadis  yang memiliki kelebihan spiritual. Tapi apa kalian tau masa lalunya? Seperti apa Indriya hingga bisa sekuat sekarang? Semua akan diungkap di komik <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil\" target=\"_blank\">Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam komik ini, kita akan diajak untuk melihat masa lalu Indriya, hingga dia bisa bertumbuh menjadi wanita kuat. Cerita tentang bagaimana Indriya memiliki kemampuan untuk berhubungan dengan makhluk dari dunia lain. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56753\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/attachment/8-140/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hantu Perempuan&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hantu Perempuan_Bhurloka: Mata Indriya Kecil\" class=\"wp-image-56753\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ciayo.com/id/comic/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil (opens in a new tab)\">Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil</a> akan menjelaskan mengenai cerita Indriya setelah terbangun di rumah sakit dan kesehariannya bersama dengan &#8220;mata baru&#8221;nya. Bagaimana cara Indriya beradaptasi setelah ibunya tewas. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Keci (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ciayo.com/id/comic/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil\" target=\"_blank\">Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Keci</a>l bisa dibilang adalah sebuah Prequel dari komik <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Bhurloka (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ciayo.com/id/comic/bhurloka\" target=\"_blank\">Bhurloka</a> yang sebelumnya sudah pernah tayang di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics</a>. Bercerita mengenai kisah Indriya yang beranjak dewasa yang menjalani kehidupannya menyucikan roh (Niraga) dan membasmi roh jahat (Nirjiva) sekaligus mengungkap kenyataan tragedi 15 tahun silam yang menewaskan ibunya. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56752\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/attachment/7-172/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jejak Darah&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1.jpg\" alt=\"Jejak Darah_Bhurloka: Mata Indriya Kecil\" class=\"wp-image-56752\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam komik ini, Lewat mata seorang Indriya kecil, kita akan melihat dunia yang sebenarnya. Di mana kengerian, ketakutan, hingga amarah berkumpul jadi satu. Semua di kumpulan kisah masa kecil Indriya. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bhurloka : Mata Indriya Kecil sudah bisa kamu nikmati di CIAYO Comics setiap hari Minggu dengan format yang berbeda dari sebelumnya. Komik bergenre horror ini tampil dengan special format yaitu komik interaktif, di mana kamu bisa merasakan sensasi membaca komik seperti membaca novel. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"56755\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/bhurloka-mata-indriya-kecil-ketika-mata-melihat-dunia-yang-berbeda/attachment/10-96/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/10-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&